# Operator-initiated clear of latched safety states.
# Contract: ICD-SAF-002. Server: safety_monitor (SRS-SAF-001).
#
# Never forces a clear: if any latched trigger condition is still active,
# the response is success=false with the active condition in `reason`.

# Request: empty.
---
bool success
# Empty on success; on failure, identifies the still-active latched
# condition (e.g. "tilt_exceeded") so the app can prompt the operator
# with a specific recovery action.
string reason
